_sText: Thanks to [BoardER](http://www.gamebanana.com/members/1263563 "") for fixing the map! ------------------ ------------------ Heya guys! I am releasing my re-make of one of my favorite GG maps, GG_Minecraft. This version of the map includes a slightly changed layout and a scale that represents the textures and Minecraft more closely. As well as structure changes, I added new textures and a new skybox that are packaged in the map. This map uses the texture pack made by [Dampfnudel](http://gamebanana.com/members/1240890) and myself. I have contacted the original map's creator but I have received no reply. I can remove the map if requested by the author. ------------------ ------------------
